section.help
  h2 Help
  p Click on the generators at the top to create random new sounds.
  p Rename your sounds by clicking on their names in the collection list.
  p 
    | Download an embeddable player with the ⏬.js button. You can include the 
    | script in your web page and play your sounds by calling `FXZ.play("laser")`
    | or whatever your sound is named.
  p Download your sound pack with the ⏬.fxx button.
  p Load your sound pack by dragging and dropping your .fxx file in the editor.
  p Export individual sounds to wav with the ⏬.wav buttons.
  p Export .fxz files for each sound with the ⏬.fxz buttons.
  p Import individual sounds by dropping .fxz files in the editor.
  h2 About
  p 
