    a(href="https://danielx.net") Daniel X. Moore
    | , inspired by sfxr
    a(href="http://www.drpetter.se/project_sfxr.html") (thanks Dr. Petter!)
    | .
    | It was a port of a port, but I decided to go ham on the binary format and
    | the embeddable synthesizer.
